name: Diamond Millionaire
description:
These Nails Will Definitely Add Some Glamour! Featuring Pearly Silver Tones With Gorgeous Glitter And Individually Hand Placed Crystals.

Each Pack Contains -
10 Hand Painted False Nails
Individual Tube Of Nail Glue

Nails Are Only Available In One Size, These Tend To Fit Most People's Natural Nail Fine, However They Can Be Filed To Suit You're Shape If Necessary. 

Nails Are Triple Top-Coated For Maximum Protection, With Only Top Quality Polishes And Products Used.
